ContainerServicesOperationsExtensions.Delete Method

Definition

Namespace:
Microsoft.Azure.Management.Compute.Fluent
Assembly:
Microsoft.Azure.Management.Compute.Fluent.dll

In this Article

Deletes the specified container service.

public static void Delete (this Microsoft.Azure.Management.Compute.Fluent.IContainerServicesOperations operations, string resourceGroupName, string containerServiceName);
Parameters
operations
IContainerServicesOperations

The operations group for this extension method.

resourceGroupName
String

The name of the resource group.

containerServiceName
String

The name of the container service in the specified subscription and resource group.

Remarks

Deletes the specified container service in the specified subscription and resource group. The operation does not delete other resources created as part of creating a container service, including storage accounts, VMs, and availability sets. All the other resources created with the container service are part of the same resource group and can be deleted individually.
